g.title: \l\lfrom werkzeug.routing import Map, Rule, NotFound, RequestRedirect\l\lurl_map = Map([\l----Rule('/', endpoint='blog/index'),\l----Rule('/<int:year>/', endpoint='blog/archive'),\l----Rule('/<int:year>/<int:month>/', endpoint='blog/archive'),\l----Rule('/<int:year>/<int:month>/<int:day>/', endpoint='blog/archive'),\l----Rule('/<int:year>/<int:month>/<int:day>/<slug>', \l endpoint='blog/show_post'),\l----Rule('/about', endpoint='blog/about_me'),\l----Rule('/feeds/', endpoint='blog/feeds'),\l----Rule('/feeds/<feed_name>.rss', endpoint='blog/show_feed')\l])\l\ldef application(environ, start_response):\l\l----urls = url_map.bind_to_environ(environ)\l----try:\l--------endpoint, args = urls.match()\l----except HTTPException, e:\l--------return e(environ, start_response)\l----start_response('200 OK', [('Content-Type', 'text/plain')])\l----return ['Rule points to %r with arguments %r' % (endpoint, args)]\l
g.text: from werkzeug.routing import Map, Rule, NotFound, RequestRedirect
